Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.util

Some utility classes, including KeyStore management, String utils, Reactive4Java extensions, etc.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Base64
    Encodes and decodes to and from Base64 notation.
    Base64.InputStream
    A Base64.InputStream will read data from another java.io.InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    Base64.OutputStream
    A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another java.io.OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    BCrypt
    BCrypt implements OpenBSD-style Blowfish password hashing using the scheme described in "A Future-Adaptable Password Scheme" by Niels Provos and David Mazieres.
    CachedThreadPoolScheduler
    The scheduler uses a cached thread pool executor (via Executors.newCachedThreadPool()) as its backing thread pool.
    DistinguishedName
    Builds or splits a distinguished name specification into components.
    KeystoreManager
    Manges keystore specific operations.
    NewThreadScheduler
    A scheduler which creates separate new threads for each task.
    ReactiveEx
    Extension methods to the Reactive4Java operators for now.
    Strings
    String utilities.
    Triplet<A,B,C>
    A three element tuple.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    KeystoreFault
    An unchecked runtime exception used to report the keystore and key management related exceptions.
